cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV

This paper is focused on cross-lingual natural language processing tasks, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also proposes a novel language distance measure based on embeddings, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The study also involves large-scale experiments and empirical evaluations, which could be relevant to neural networks (cs.NE) and computer vision (cs.CV) sub-categories.
